  "What does 'optimization' mean in calculus?": "\"优化\"在微积分中意味着什么?",
  "Graphing the function accurately": "精确构造函数",
  "Finding where the function equals zero": "查找函数等于零的函数",
  "Making a function faster": "使功能更快",
  "Finding the maximum or minimum value of a function, often subject to constraints": "确定一个职能的最高或最低价值,往往受限制",
  "Optimization uses derivatives to find where a function attains its maximum or minimum value. Set f'(x) = 0 and check whether the critical point is a max, min, or neither.": "优化利用衍生物查找函数达到其最大值或最小值的位置。设定 f'(x) = 0 并检查关键点是否为最大值、最小值或最小值。",
  "What is a 'critical point'?": "什么是“临界点”?",
  "A point where f'(x) = 0 or f'(x) is undefined": "F'(x) = 0 或 f'(x) 未定义的点",
  "The endpoints of the domain": "域域的终点",
  "A point where f is discontinuous": "f 是连续的点",
  "A point where f(x) = 0": "f(x) = 0 的点",
  "Critical points are where f'(x) = 0 or f'(x) doesn't exist. Local maxima and minima can only occur at critical points (or endpoints of a closed interval).": "关键点是不存在 f'(x) = 0 或 f'(x) 的 关键点。 本地最大值和微型值只能在关键点( 或封闭间隔的终点) 出现 。",
  "What is the 'closed interval method' for finding absolute extrema?": "找到绝对极限的“ 封闭间隔方法” 是什么 ?",
  "Use the second derivative test at every point according to widely held views on this topic": "根据对本专题广泛持有的意见,在每一阶段使用第二次衍生产品检验标准",
  "Only check where f'(x) = 0 under most circumstances involving absolute": "只检查在多数涉及绝对的情况下f'(x)=0=0",
  "Only check the endpoints under most circumstances involving absolute": "在大多数涉及绝对值的情况下只检查端点",
  "Evaluate f at critical points and endpoints; the largest is the absolute max, smallest is the absolute min": "在关键点和终点评价f;最大是绝对最大,最小是绝对分钟",
  "On a closed interval [a,b]: find all critical points, evaluate f at each critical point and at both endpoints. Compare values to find the absolute maximum and minimum.": "在封闭间隔[a,b]:找到所有临界点,在每个临界点和两个端点对f进行评价。比较数值以找到绝对最大和最小值。",
  "What does the 'second derivative test' determine?": "“第二次衍生物试验”决定什么?",
  "The absolute maximum and minimum": "绝对上限和最低",
  "Whether the function is increasing or decreasing": "职能是增加还是减少",
  "Whether a critical point is a local max (f'' < 0) or local min (f'' > 0)": "临界点是本地最大值(f''最高值 < 0)还是本地分钟(f''>0)",
  "Whether the function is concave up or down everywhere": "函数是向上还是向下 。",
  "At a critical point where f'(c) = 0: if f''(c) > 0, it's a local minimum; if f''(c) < 0, it's a local maximum; if f''(c) = 0, the test is inconclusive.": "在f'(c) = 0的临界点:如果f'(c) > 0,是当地最低限值;如果f'(c) < 0,是当地最高限值;如果f'(c) = 0,则测试无结果。",
  "What does 'constraint' mean in optimization?": "\"约束\"在优化中意味着什么?",
  "The derivative of the objective function": "目标职能的衍生物",
  "The domain of the function": "函数的域域",
  "The function to be maximized": "要最大化的函数",
  "A condition that limits the possible values of the variables": "限制变量可能值的条件",
  "A constraint is an equation or inequality that the variables must satisfy (like 'the perimeter is 40' or 'the volume is 1000'). Use it to eliminate a variable before optimizing.": "制约是变量必须满足的方程式或不平等(如“周界为40”或“体积为1000”)。在优化前,使用它来消除变量。",
  "What is an 'objective function'?": "什么是“客观功能”?",
