  "The objective function is the quantity you want to optimize (maximize or minimize), such as area, cost, profit, or distance.": "目标函数是您想要优化的数量(最大化或最小化),如面积、成本、利润或距离。",
  "What is a 'local maximum'?": "什么是“本地最大”?",
  "The largest value of f on its entire domain": "F在其整个领域的最大价值",
  "A point where f(c) is larger than f(x) for all x near c": "f(c) 所有 x 接近 c 的 f(x) 点大于 f(x) 的 f(c) 值",
  "A point where f'(c) > 0": "f'(c) > 0 的点",
  "A point where f(c) > 0": "f(c) > 0 的点",
  "A local maximum at x = c means f(c) >= f(x) for all x in some neighborhood of c. It's the highest point locally, though not necessarily the highest on the entire domain.": "x = c 的本地最大值表示所有 x 在 c 的某个附近 的 f(c) = f(x) 。 这是本地最高点, 但不一定是整个域的最高点 。",
  "What does 'absolute minimum' mean?": "\"绝对最低\"是什么意思?",
  "The smallest value of f(x) over its entire domain": "F(x) 在整个域域中最小值的 f(x) 值",
  "The smallest positive value of f": "f 最小正值",
  "Where f'(x) is smallest": "f'(x) 最小的",
  "The absolute (global) minimum is the smallest value f achieves on its entire domain. On a closed interval, it occurs at a critical point or an endpoint.": "绝对值( Global) 最小值是 f 在其整个域上达到的最小值。 关闭间隔时, 它会发生在一个关键点或终点 。",
  "What does 'feasible region' mean in optimization?": "“可行区域”在优化方面意味着什么?",
  "Where the derivative is positive": "当衍生物呈正值时",
