  "The graph of the objective function": "目标函数图",
  "The range of the function": "函数范围",
  "The feasible region is the set of all (x, y, ...) values that satisfy all given constraints. The optimal solution must lie within this region.": "可行的区域是能够满足所有既定限制的所有(x、y、...)价值的一组价值,最佳解决办法必须在这个区域内。",
  "What does 'endpoint' mean for optimization on an interval?": "在间隔内优化“ 端点” 意味着什么 ?",
