  "A wire of length 100 cm is cut into two pieces. One forms a square, the other a circle. How should it be cut to minimize total enclosed area?": "长100厘米的线条被切成两块。 一条形成方形, 另一条形成圆形。 如何切开线条以尽量减少总封闭面积 ?",
