  "Run the entire beach then swim": "跑遍整个海滩 然后游泳",
  "The optimal entry point balances running speed vs swimming speed. Setting dt/dx = 0 involves 1/4 = (60-x)/sqrt((60-x)^2+1600), which uses Snell's law type reasoning.": "最佳切入点平衡运行速度与游泳速度。 设置 dt/ dx = 0 涉及 1/4 = ( 60- x) / sqrt (( 60- x) 2+1600) , 使用 Snell 的法律类型推理 。",
  "A farmer wants to build a rectangular pen with an internal divider, using 800 m of fencing. What dimensions maximize the total area?": "农民想用800米的栅栏,用内部隔开器建造长方形钢笔。",
  "160 m x 160 m": "160米x160米",
  "133 m x 200 m": "133米x200米",
  "100 m x 200 m": "100米x200米",
  "3w + 2l = 800. l = (800-3w)/2. A = wl = w(400-1.5w). A' = 400-3w = 0, w = 400/3. Hmm, that gives non-integer. Let me re-examine: if the divider is parallel to width, then 2l + 3w = 800. l = (800-3w)/2 = 400-1.5w. A = w(400-1.5w). A' = 400-3w = 0, w = 400/3 approximately 133.3, l = 200. A = (400/3)(200) = 80000/3.": "3w + 2l = 800. l = 800. l = (800-3w)/2. A = wl = w (400-1.5w). A = 400-3w = 0, w = 400/3. hmm , 提供非内插值。 让我重新审查:如果分离器与宽度平行,则2l + 3w = 800. l = (800-3w)/2 = 400-1.5w. A = (400-1.5w). A = 400-3w = 0, w = 400/3 约133.3, l = 200. A = (400/3) (200) = 800000/3。",
  "An isosceles triangle has perimeter 30 cm. What dimensions maximize its area?": "等星三角形有30厘米的周界。 哪些维度使面积最大化?",
  "Base 5, sides 12.5": "基地5,两侧12.5",
