  "Base 10, sides 10": "基地10,双方10",
  "An equilateral triangle with sides 10 cm each": "方形三角形,每边10厘米",
  "For a fixed perimeter, the triangle with maximum area is equilateral. With P = 30, each side = 10 cm. Area = (sqrt(3)/4)*100 = 25sqrt(3) cm^2.": "对于固定周界,三角形与最大面积是等值的。P=30,每侧=10厘米。区域=(sqrt(3)/4)*100=25sqrt(3)cm2)。",
  "A school wants to build a rectangular running track with two semicircular ends. The total perimeter must be 400 m. What dimensions maximize the rectangular area inside?": "学校想要建一个长方形运行轨迹, 有两个半圆形端。 总周界必须是400米。 什么样的维度能使长方形区域最大化 ?",
  "Length 100 m, diameter = 200/pi m": "长度100米,直径=200皮米",
  "Length = 100 m, width = 400/(2pi) m": "长度 = 100米,宽 = 400/(2pi) m",
  "Equal length and width": "相同长度和宽度",
